<HEAD>People in the News</HEAD>
<HEAD>Eds: CORRECTS spelling of Webber in first item.</HEAD>
<HEAD>LaserPhoto NY44</HEAD>
<DATELINE>MOSCOW (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Britain's Prince Edward arrived Saturday for a
three-day visit during which he will attend a play put on by a
British theater troupe.
   The 25-year-old son of Queen Elizabeth II will attend T.S.
Eliot's ``Murder in the Cathedral'' on Sunday.
   The play is being staged by Britain's National Youth Theater, of
